    5:

    7:         , get_other_end_case/1
    8:         , is_end_stop_case/1

   10:         , contains_stop_case/1
   11:         , get_neighbors_case/1

   14:         , get_intersection_case/1]).

   19:         , end_per_group/2
   20:         , init_per_testcase/2
   21:         , end_per_testcase/2]).
   22: 
   23: all() ->
   24:   [ {group, three_stops}
   25:   , {group, four_stops}
   26:   , {group, five_stops}
   27:   , {group, nine_stops}
   28:   ].
   29: 
   30: groups() ->
   31:   [ { three_stops
   32:     , []
   33:     , [ get_next_stop_case
   34:       , get_other_end_case
   35:       , is_end_stop_case
   36:       , get_number_case
   37:       ]
   38:     }
   39:   , { four_stops
   40:     , []
   41:     , [ contains_stop_case
   42:       ]
   43:     }
   44:   , { five_stops
   45:     , []
   46:     , [ get_neighbors_case
   47:       , get_duration_case
   48:       , get_target_case
   49:       ]
   50:     }
   51:   , { nine_stops
   52:     , []
   53:     , [ get_intersection_case
   54:       ]
   55:     }
   56:   ].
   57: 
   58: init_per_group(three_stops, Config) ->
   59:   Stop1 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop1, strict),
   60:   Stop2 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop2, strict),
   61:   Stop3 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop3, strict),
   62:   Dur1_2 = 7,
   63:   Dur2_3 = 11,
   64:   Config ++ [ {stop1, Stop1}
   65:             , {stop2, Stop2}
   66:             , {stop3, Stop3}
   67:             , {dur1_2, Dur1_2}
   68:             , {dur2_3, Dur2_3}
   69:             ];
   70: 
   71: init_per_group(four_stops, Config) ->
   72:   Stop4 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop4, strict),
   73:   init_per_group(three_stops, Config) ++[{stop4, Stop4}];
   74: 
   75: init_per_group(five_stops, Config) ->
   76:   Stop5 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop5, strict),
   77:   Dur3_4 = 13,
   78:   Dur4_5 = 17,
   79:   init_per_group(four_stops, Config) ++ [ {stop5, Stop5}
   80:                                         , {dur3_4, Dur3_4}
   81:                                         , {dur4_5, Dur4_5}
   82:                                         ];
   83: 
   84: init_per_group(nine_stops, Config) ->
   85:   Stop6 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop6, strict),
   86:   Stop7 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop7, strict),
   87:   Stop8 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop8, strict),
   88:   Stop9 = gen_server_mock:start(stop, stop9, strict),
   89:   init_per_group(five_stops, Config) ++ [ {stop6, Stop6}
   90:                                         , {stop7, Stop7}
   91:                                         , {stop8, Stop8}
   92:                                         , {stop9, Stop9}
   93:                                         ];
   94: 
   95: init_per_group(_Group, Config) ->
   96:   Config.
   97: 
   98: 
   99: end_per_group(three_stops, Config) ->
  100:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  101:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  102:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  103:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop1)),
  104:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop2)),
  105:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop3)),
  106:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop1),
  107:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop2),
  108:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop3);
  109: 
  110: end_per_group(four_stops, Config) ->
  111:   end_per_group(three_stops, Config),
  112:   Stop4 = ?config(stop4, Config),
  113:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop4)),
  114:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop4);
  115: 
  116: end_per_group(five_stops, Config) ->
  117:   end_per_group(four_stops, Config),
  118:   Stop5 = ?config(stop5, Config),
  119:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop5)),
  120:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop5);
  121: 
  122: end_per_group(nine_stops, Config) ->
  123:   end_per_group(five_stop, Config),
  124:   Stop6 = ?config(stop6, Config),
  125:   Stop7 = ?config(stop7, Config),
  126:   Stop8 = ?config(stop8, Config),
  127:   Stop9 = ?config(stop9, Config),
  128:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop6)),
  129:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop7)),
  130:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop8)),
  131:   ?assert(gen_server_mock:validate(Stop9)),
  132:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop6),
  133:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop7),
  134:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop8),
  135:   gen_server_mock:stop(Stop9);
  136: 
  137: end_per_group(_Group, _Config) ->
  138:   ok.
  139: 
  140: 
  141: init_per_testcase(TestCase, Config) ->
  142:   line_supervisor:start_link(),
  143:   Config.
  144: 
  145: 
  146: end_per_testcase(_TestCase, Config) ->
  147:   Config.
  148: 
  149: 
  150: get_next_stop_case(Config) ->
  151:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  152:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  153:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  154:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  155:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  156:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3], bus),
  157: 
  158:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEXT_STOP(Line, Stop3, Stop1), {Stop2, Dur1_2}),
  159:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEXT_STOP(Line, Stop3, Stop2), {Stop3, Dur2_3}),
  160:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEXT_STOP(Line, Stop3, Stop3), none),
  161:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEXT_STOP(Line, Stop1, Stop3), {Stop2, Dur2_3}),
  162:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEXT_STOP(Line, Stop1, Stop2), {Stop1, Dur1_2}),
  163:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEXT_STOP(Line, Stop1, Stop1), none),
  164: 
  165:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  166: 
  167: 
  168: get_other_end_case(Config) ->
  169:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  170:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  171:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  172:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  173:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  174:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3], bus),
  175: 
  176:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_OTHER_END(Line, Stop1), Stop3),
  177:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_OTHER_END(Line, Stop3), Stop1),
  178: 
  179:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  180: 
  181: 
  182: is_end_stop_case(Config) ->
  183:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  184:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  185:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  186:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  187:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  188:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3], bus),
  189: 
  190:   ?assertEqual(true, line:?IS_END_STOP(Line, Stop1)),
  191:   ?assertEqual(false, line:?IS_END_STOP(Line, Stop2)),
  192:   ?assertEqual(true, line:?IS_END_STOP(Line, Stop3)),
  193: 
  194:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  195: 
  196: 
  197: get_number_case(Config) ->
  198:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  199:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  200:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  201:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  202:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  203:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3], bus),
  204: 
  205:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NUMBER(Line), 1),
  206: 
  207:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  208: 
  209: 
  210: contains_stop_case(Config) ->
  211:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  212:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  213:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  214:   Stop4 = ?config(stop4, Config),
  215:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  216:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  217:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3], bus),
  218: 
  219:   ?assertEqual(true, line:?CONTAINS_STOP(Line, Stop1)),
  220:   ?assertEqual(true, line:?CONTAINS_STOP(Line, Stop2)),
  221:   ?assertEqual(true, line:?CONTAINS_STOP(Line, Stop3)),
  222:   ?assertEqual(false, line:?CONTAINS_STOP(Line, Stop4)),
  223: 
  224:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  225: 
  226: 
  227: get_neighbors_case(Config) ->
  228:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  229:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  230:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  231:   Stop4 = ?config(stop4, Config),
  232:   Stop5 = ?config(stop5, Config),
  233:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  234:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  235:   Dur3_4 = ?config(dur3_4, Config),
  236:   Dur4_5 = ?config(dur4_5, Config),
  237:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3, Dur3_4, Stop4, Dur4_5, Stop5], bus),
  238:   
  239:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEIGHBORS(Line, Stop1), [{Stop2, Dur1_2, Stop5, Line}]),
  240:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEIGHBORS(Line, Stop2), [{Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop1, Line}, {Stop3, Dur2_3, Stop5, Line}]),
  241:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEIGHBORS(Line, Stop3), [{Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop1, Line}, {Stop4, Dur3_4, Stop5, Line}]),
  242:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEIGHBORS(Line, Stop4), [{Stop3, Dur3_4, Stop1, Line}, {Stop5, Dur4_5, Stop5, Line}]),
  243:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_NEIGHBORS(Line, Stop5), [{Stop4, Dur4_5, Stop1, Line}]),
  244: 
  245:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  246: 
  247: 
  248: get_duration_case(Config) ->
  249:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  250:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  251:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  252:   Stop4 = ?config(stop4, Config),
  253:   Stop5 = ?config(stop5, Config),
  254:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  255:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  256:   Dur3_4 = ?config(dur3_4, Config),
  257:   Dur4_5 = ?config(dur4_5, Config),
  258:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3, Dur3_4, Stop4, Dur4_5, Stop5], bus),
  259: 
  260:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop1, Stop2), Dur1_2),
  261:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop1, Stop3), Dur1_2 + Dur2_3),
  262:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop1, Stop4), Dur1_2 + Dur2_3 + Dur3_4),
  263:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop1, Stop5), Dur1_2 + Dur2_3 + Dur3_4 + Dur4_5),
  264:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop2, Stop3), Dur2_3),
  265:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop2, Stop4), Dur2_3 + Dur3_4),
  266:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop2, Stop5), Dur2_3 + Dur3_4 + Dur4_5),
  267:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop3, Stop4), Dur3_4),
  268:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop3, Stop5), Dur3_4 + Dur4_5),
  269:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop4, Stop5), Dur4_5),
  270: 
  271:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop2, Stop1), Dur1_2),
  272:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop3, Stop1), Dur1_2 + Dur2_3),
  273:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop4, Stop1), Dur1_2 + Dur2_3 + Dur3_4),
  274:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop5, Stop1), Dur1_2 + Dur2_3 + Dur3_4 + Dur4_5),
  275:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop3, Stop2), Dur2_3),
  276:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop4, Stop2), Dur2_3 + Dur3_4),
  277:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop5, Stop2), Dur2_3 + Dur3_4 + Dur4_5),
  278:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop4, Stop3), Dur3_4),
  279:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop5, Stop3), Dur3_4 + Dur4_5),
  280:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_DURATION(Line, Stop5, Stop4), Dur4_5),
  281: 
  282:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  283: 
  284: 
  285: get_target_case(Config) ->
  286:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  287:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  288:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  289:   Stop4 = ?config(stop4, Config),
  290:   Stop5 = ?config(stop5, Config),
  291:   Dur1_2 = ?config(dur1_2, Config),
  292:   Dur2_3 = ?config(dur2_3, Config),
  293:   Dur3_4 = ?config(dur3_4, Config),
  294:   Dur4_5 = ?config(dur4_5, Config),
  295:   Line = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, Dur1_2, Stop2, Dur2_3, Stop3, Dur3_4, Stop4, Dur4_5, Stop5], bus),
  296: 
  297:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_TARGET(Line, Stop1, Stop3), Stop5),
  298:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_TARGET(Line, Stop5, Stop3), Stop1),
  299:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_TARGET(Line, Stop3, Stop4), Stop5),
  300:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_TARGET(Line, Stop3, Stop2), Stop1),
  301: 
  302:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line).
  303: 
  304: 
  305: get_intersection_case(Config) ->
  306:   Stop1 = ?config(stop1, Config),
  307:   Stop2 = ?config(stop2, Config),
  308:   Stop3 = ?config(stop3, Config),
  309:   Stop4 = ?config(stop4, Config),
  310:   Stop5 = ?config(stop5, Config),
  311:   Stop6 = ?config(stop6, Config),
  312:   Stop7 = ?config(stop7, Config),
  313:   Stop8 = ?config(stop8, Config),
  314:   Stop9 = ?config(stop9, Config),
  315:   Line1 = line_supervisor:start_line(1, [Stop1, 5, Stop2, 5, Stop3], bus),
  316:   Line2 = line_supervisor:start_line(2, [Stop4, 5, Stop2, 5, Stop5], bus),
  317:   Line3 = line_supervisor:start_line(3, [Stop1, 5, Stop6, 5, Stop7], bus),
  318:   Line4 = line_supervisor:start_line(4, [Stop8, 5, Stop9, 5, Stop7], bus),
  319: 
  320:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line1, Line2), Stop2),
  321:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line2, Line1), Stop2),
  322:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line1, Line3), Stop1),
  323:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line3, Line1), Stop1),
  324:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line3, Line4), Stop7),
  325:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line4, Line3), Stop7),
  326: 
  327:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line1, Line4), none),
  328:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line4, Line1), none),
  329:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line2, Line3), none),
  330:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line3, Line2), none),
  331:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line2, Line4), none),
  332:   ?assertEqual(line:?GET_INTERSECTION(Line4, Line2), none),
  333: 
  334:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line1),
  335:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line2),
  336:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line3),
  337:   line_supervisor:stop_line(Line4).
